with someone you're comfortable with.

264
00:20:59,731 --> 00:21:01,101
It tastes sweet.

265
00:21:03,251 --> 00:21:05,501
The group you're managing
is Sparkling, right?

266
00:21:05,801 --> 00:21:07,741
It seems like
they're getting good word of mouth.

267
00:21:07,831 --> 00:21:09,901
Not so much. They're not doing good.

268
00:21:10,341 --> 00:21:12,231
If they can't make a hit song
in their third year,

269
00:21:12,981 --> 00:21:14,341
it'll be the end of them.

270
00:21:24,681 --> 00:21:25,911
Are you coming back?

271
00:21:26,221 --> 00:21:28,111
You must've gotten an awesome song.

272
00:21:28,461 --> 00:21:30,001
-No.
-Or did you get an investor?

273
