275
00:21:35,811 --> 00:21:37,481
Because SHAX isn't causing any trouble,

276
00:21:37,571 --> 00:21:39,241
they just want a newsmaker.

277
00:21:40,081 --> 00:21:42,191
Those lazy pigs. They never do their job.

278
00:21:42,761 --> 00:21:44,921
I'll look for newsworthy material.

279
00:21:45,011 --> 00:21:46,151
What about Ryok?

280
00:21:46,241 --> 00:21:47,911
He got back home after the shoot.

281
00:21:48,001 --> 00:21:50,071
It's been three years,
and he's been getting treated.

282
00:21:50,161 --> 00:21:51,651
so he must've gotten better.

283
00:21:51,741 --> 00:21:54,291
But keep your eye on him.
He could break down all at once.

284
00:21:55,131 --> 00:21:58,561
He's the only one
who's making big money for us.

285
00:21:58,651 --> 00:21:59,701
Yes, sir.

